<html>

<head>
	<title>Stashflip - BUY AND RESELL</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css" />
</head>

<body>
	<div id="search_bar">
		<%= render :partial => 'searchbar' %>		 
	</div>
	
	<div id="maincontent">

			<div id="main_top">
				<div id="main_bottom_info">
				<div id="main_bottom_info_left">
					<div class="main_title">
					Maximize your profit by buying and reselling.
					</div>
					<div class="main_text"><br/>
					Stashflip is built for those looking to make money by buying and reselling online. Buy and sell on Ebay, Amazon, or Craigslist to maximize your earnings. Buying and flipping is the name of the game.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div ="main_bottom_info_right">
					<img src="/images/featureinfo1.png" />
				</div>
				</div>
				
				<div id="main_bottom_info">
				<div id="main_bottom_info_left">
					<div class="main_title">
					Get on your grind.
					</div>
					<div class="main_text"><br/>
					By aggregating the best deals on the web, we drop knowledge on how to improve your hustle. It provides an easily accessible estimate on how much money you can make on that item.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div ="main_bottom_info_right">
					<img src="/images/featureinfo2.png" />
				</div>
				</div>
				
				<div id="main_bottom_info">
				<div id="main_bottom_info_left">
					<div class="main_title">
					Submit Deals
					</div>
					<div class="main_text"><br/>
					Submit deals to <b>stashflip at gmail.com</b> when you have leads on what you were able to flip. We will add in additional ways to submit deals later on.
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				
				<div id="main_bottom_info">
				<div id="main_bottom_info_left">
					<div class="main_title">
					Staff
					</div>
					<div class="main_text"><br/>
					Stashflip is a fourth year student at the University of California. E-mail me at <b>stashflip at gmail.com</b>.
					</div>
				</div>
				<div ="main_bottom_info_right">
					<img src="/images/staff.png" />
				</div>
				</div>			
				
			</div> 
			
			<div id="main_right">
				<%= render :partial => '/deals/adroll' %>
			</div>           	  	

		<%= render :partial => 'website/statcounter' %>
		<%= render :partial => 'website/footer' %>

	</div><!--end maincontent-->
	
</body>

